I’m progressing steadily across all three languages, with significant growth in Python and consistent improvement in Java and C through hands-on projects.
I rarely need help but reach out when I’m stuck on more complex bugs, especially in C or Java. I’m independent in solving most issues, but I always value feedback from code reviews or peers.

I’m highly confident in Python, having used it for automation, data analysis, and web scraping, same in Java and C, applying both for software design and systems programming. I’ve developed multiple projects in all three, from backend services in Java to low-level memory management in C.
